articles.title: Independent prognostic factors predicting survival in multiple myeloma patients post-chemotherapy: a retrospective study.
articles.summary: In multiple myeloma patients, certain clinical factors like age, disease stage, and treatment response can help predict patient survival after chemotherapy.

articles.title: Endobronchial ultrasound-guided mediastinal biopsies for the diagnosis of mediastinal diseases: A network meta-analysis.
articles.summary: A network meta-analysis shows endobronchial ultrasound-guided biopsies effectively diagnose mediastinal diseases, particularly in lung cancer staging.
